data.description: Located in the prestigious Bay Club of Beach Haven this free-standing condo offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, inground pool and reversed living to maximize the bay views.  The sun splashed living area features an open concept plan, vaulted ceiling and pergo style floors.  Kitchen upgrades such as a tiled backsplash, stainless steel appliances, 5 seat breakfast bar, granite counters, soft close drawers, built in wine rack, and beverage cooler make it a joy to prepare meals.  The large dining room has space for the whole family and adjacent rear deck has a hard gas line for your barbecue grill.  Master bedroom amenities include crown molding, walk in closet, private covered deck, and en-suite bathroom with tiled shower and double pedestal sinks.  With 2 zone gas heat, central AC, Navien tankless water heater and front-loading washer/dryer this beach house can be enjoyed all year long.  Keep all of your beach accessories in the attached garage with tiled floor and bonus room.  The public boat ramp is conveniently located next door as well as basketball court and gazebo.  Walk or bicycle to everything that LBI has to offer like shopping, nightlife, top class restaurants, amusements, mini golf, ice cream and more.
